    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, chop the <strong>paneer</strong> into bite-sized cubes</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the<strong> cubed paneer </strong>and cook for 3-5 min until golden, turning occasionally for even colouring</p><p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>golden paneer</strong> to a plate and set aside, reserve the pan</p>",
