      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>green</strong> <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
