    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, stir through the <strong>blanched peas </strong>and <strong>browned paneer </strong>and cook for 1 min to warm everything through</p><p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir through <strong>half </strong>the <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>mattar paneer</strong></p>",
