    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mattar paneer</strong> over the <strong>sultana rice</strong></p><p>Dollop the <strong>coriander chutney</strong> and <strong>remaining natural yoghurt </strong>all over</p><p>Garnish with any <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
